1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:09,000
Criminals around the world are dying one after another from heart attacks.

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:16,500
On the internet, it seems they are calling
the one causing this phenomenon "Kira."

3
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:24,000
At the request of the ICPO, I have been assigned to investigate this case.

4
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:31,500
I am L. If someone is judging criminals,
then that person is also a criminal.

5
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:39,000
Kira, I want to ask you.
Is what you are doing truly justice?

6
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:46,500
This man... Lind L. Tailor?
There is no way L would appear in public.

7
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:54,000
I will find you without fail.
I will prove that I am justice.

8
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:01,500
I'll take the bait.
If I write this man's name, I'll learn L's true identity.

9
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:09,000
Tailor has died. It was a heart attack.

10
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:16,500
So Kira really can kill.
However, that was not me just now.

11
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:24,000
Kira, that just now confirmed it.
You have the ability to kill people.

12
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:31,500
What... It was a trap!
That man was a stand-in for L!

13
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:39,000
Furthermore, I have obtained crucial information.
Kira is in the Kanto region.

14
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:46,500
This broadcast was limited to the Kanto region.
The fact that you reacted means you are there.

15
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:54,000
He got me... I fell completely into L's trap.

16
00:01:57,000 --> 00:02:01,500
But I will not give up.
Whoever L may be, I will eliminate him.

17
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:09,000
L, in this battle, I will be the one who wins in the end.

18
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:16,500
Kira versus L. An unprecedented battle of wits
between two geniuses has begun.

19
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:24,000
Which side holds justice?
No one can say for certain.
